article.description: — Matt Balanc had 20 points as Quinnipiac beat Marist 94-87 on Friday night.
article.headline: Balanc scores 20 to lead Quinnipiac over Marist 94-87
article.linkText: Balanc scores 20 to lead Quinnipiac over Marist 94-87
article.story: HAMDEN, Conn. -- — Matt Balanc had 20 points as Quinnipiac beat Marist 94-87 on Friday night. Balanc made 5 of 7 3-pointers. Kevin Marfo had 17 points for Quinnipiac (11-7, 6-4 Metro Atlantic Athletic Conference). Tymu Chenery added 14 points. Dezi Jones had 13 points. Noah Harris scored a season-high 24 points for the Red Foxes (8-11, 3-7). Jao Ituka added 14 points. Ricardo Wright had 13 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
